spanGrp.span: _ I am Nana Khabuliani from Mutsdi.
nana xabuliani-zurabianisa (svanuri enis oluruli dialekis carmomadgeneli); medea saliani (svanuri enis balskvemouri dialekis carmomadgeneli) zurabianebis gvari.
Speaker: Nana Khabuliani (CH); interviewer: Medea Saghliani (LB). The Zurabians' clan. Video 29; (00:37:34:440_00:41:01:360).
lucile xi lpte, zuri zurabyn ardaanis e.
I am married in Chvelpi; I am the wife of Zuri Zurabiani, who is the son of Ardavan Zurabiani.
gatxovili var velpi, zuri ardavanis e zurabianis meule var.
alyr lix ibe nxen carmoobit i ka meqde lix ube unte.
They come from Upper Svaneti, but later they moved to Lower one.
eseni arian carmoobit zemo svanetidan da gadmosulebi arian kvemo svaneti.
semi laxba lmrelix ka meqde amx i exu lps alzigli, mrme _ ibs i msme _ geds.
There were three brothers; they moved here: one settled in Chvelpi, another - in Tvibi and the third - in Shgedi.
sami ma qopila ("qopilan") gadmosuli ak ("aket") da erti velpi dasaxlebula, meore _ vibi da mesame _ gedi.
es'gi, alyrs dautkiat ami, ere ee sgim lok lmr mine pdyas i amx k'r emqedlix,
They said that there was sour water where they lived
ese igi, amat dautkviat ase, rom ik mave cqali qopilao mat axlos da aket rom gadmosulan,
ny lok xees ey dgis otzignd, ere ime ma... sgim lok irdi i dasaxlebulan amnen,
and, having moved here, they decided to settle down where there was sour water.
ven iset adgilas unda davsaxldeto, ("rom") sadac mave cqali iknebao da dasaxlebulan ase,
ser exu _ elps, mrme _ ibs i msme geds ri.
So, shortly, one brother lives in Chvelpi, another - in Tvibi and the third - in Shgeti.
molet erti _ velpi ("velps"), meore _ vibi da mesame gedi aris.
We gather together every year and have a session,
qoel celicads, atxe at sekembers ue grodebit amn.
this year it will be on the tenth of September.
qovel celicads, axla at sekembers uve vgrovdebit ase.
i xixryelld i zurabynrs, eey zurabynrsi ka xindrnid amxennen
We gather and invite the Zurabianis from over there as well.
evgrovdebit xolme da zurabianebs, ikaur zurabianebsac veaiebit xolme aket
i i xixryelld ibs, iritad ei lok li alyre sopel i ene gr ser ale, qriloba, at sekembers.
We gather around inTvibi; mainly it is their village; we meet on the tenth of September.
da evgrovdebit xolme vibi, e, iritadad is ariso amati sopeli da ik gvakvs uve es, qriloba, at sekembers.
xaxrylid tetrs i mag zurabynar, erys saualeba xua, i utxexen onrid i
We collect money and all Zurabianis, being able to come here, arrive from all over the area And
vagrovebt puls ("tetrs") da qvela zurabiani, visac saualeba akvs, qvela utxidan movdivart da
eenen gr ser limzr i mag.
we pray there and all like that...
ik gvakvs molet locva da qvelaperi.
_ ocdatramei clis xi, xi mi atxe i maqa oxid gezal.
_ I am thirty eight years old and I have five children.
_ ocdactvramei clis var, var me axla da mqavs xuti vili.
_ lunud reka oa lz xi, ei.
_ Tell me in Svan how old you are...
_ svanurad tkvi ramdeni clis xar, is.
_ semedixara lzy xi i maqa oxid gezal.
_ I am thirty nine years old and I have five children.
_ ocdacxramei clis var da mqavs xuti vili.
_ lzgre dsma mi ?gauear? yedara lzy otcilenxs ka, mare ekad permysa xard,
_ I have finished nothing; I got married at eighteen; I'd been on the farm before.
_ damtavrebuli araperi me ??? tvramei clis gavtxovdi, magram manamde permai viqavi ("vimqopebodi"),
limii u mun, mag, mare k'otcilenxs i ekno 'osed amnen ser i utrad.
I had a limit as well, but I've got married and remained uneducated.
limiic mkonda, qvelaperi ("qvela"), magram gavtxovdi da mere davri uve ase uscavlelad.
_ maene gezal oa lz li isgu?
_ How old is your eldest child?
_ eni uprosi ("qvelaze didi") vili ramdeni clisaa?
_ The eldest is nineteen years old.
_ Another boy, the youngest one, is ten years old.
_ meore, qvelaze umcrosi, ati clis, bii.
qini latxlisa ser exu qin gaqa i tx dina.
While searching for a boy we have had four girls.
biis ebnai ("uve, mei") erti bii gvqavs da otxi gogo.
_ Are you going to move somewhere?
_ airebt sadme gadasaxlebas ("giiriat sait samosaxlo{s}en svla")?
_ atxe gau ser, ere k'r oed saqulyte, xaired.
_ We want to go to Sakulia.
_ axla gvinda molet ("uve, mei"), rom saquliai cavidet, vairebt.
atxe amosalet suru dya li guge, mm gacqobs ex i nte er gundes mimosla,
East is too far from here; it does not fit us to go there and we want to have our way to Svaneti.
axla amosavleti meismead oria ventvis, ar gvacqobs ik (casvla) da svaneti rom gvkondes mimosvla,
In short, we want to settle down in Sakulia.
_ Why are you going from here?
_ nu, ama, ere ela amenen pdyas ri, igar ale iae gugey lras, igar esa,
_ Well, because there is a brook near here and it always takes away our hayland;
_ nu, imiom ("amistvis"), rom ele ak axlos aris, qoveltvis es iavebs vens satibs qoveltvis miakvs,
mudmid esa ser i amn gaginadgura ezoar i mag ser.
It takes it away constantly and devastates the yards and everything else;
mudmivad miakvs uve da ase gagvinadgura ezoebi da qvelaperi molet ("uve").
aal 'anpe mag i ar irs, ra, amnen lirde ser mm irs.
it hit all nut trees completely...and it makes no sense to live here further
alis xeebi qvela caakcia da ar irs, ra, ak qopna uve ar irs.
e mdgomareobys'ri, mankany 'oguure lena ats agisos.
Things are getting so that it broke our car last year, on the tenth of August.
iset mdgomareobaia, mankanac dagvimvria aran at agvisos.
e grigl anqad iknu, ere aduure mankana.
Such a storm came from above that it broke our car!
iseti grigali camovida zemodan, rom mankana dagvimvria.
eksasi dolr... usgir dolar dauda atxe ea i lisqi, 'nsqe i atxe izell,
It cost him 600 dollars... 600 dollars to repair it... and now he goes by it...
ekvsasi dolari... ekvsasi dolari dauda axla imisi gaeteba, gaaeta da axla dadis,
mare mainc ser ex xoa atxe, bopred xoa ex, ado ny aa xirdid aa ame, ans.
But still it's better for children to be there while we, adults, prefer to stay here.
magram mainc ikit sobia uve, bavvebistvis ikit sobia, torem ven isev ak viknebit, svaneti.
There was a natural disaster there in eighty seven...
nqad amelka, ladrs xalid, y, am, gugey... mdmn... i eno gaqlni, gau meyad gadasla.
An avalanche moved down from Lachvadari up to here... and since then we've been frightened and eager to leave...
amovida akedan, luvadars veaxit, zvavi akamde, vens... imamde... da imis mere gveinia, sul gvinda gadasvla.
eka daemtxa, migi muxbe... migi s atdagn muxbe, ekas sainel, aan saineli mdgomareoba iqo, eka.
Death of my brother-in-law coincided with it...It was a terrible, terrible time...
main daemtxva, emi ma,, ems kmars gardaecvala ma, main saineli, alian saineli mdgomareoba iqo, main.
mankanli ami ser lis, calebit, rakorl amnen anqidx amx.
They hardly brought cars by tractors...
mankanebic ase livs, cvalebit, rakorebit moiqvanes ("moianes") ak.
ei atxe, u gis adgnda, mare legmerde tbilis geqda, exenisa onqidd
He died at home, but being ill he was in Tbilisi and we brought him here...
("is axla") is sivdilit axla saxli gardaicvala, magram avadmqopi tbilisi gvqavda, ikidan camoviqvanet ("movianet")
i ales daemtxa eka ei, otxmocda... ardigid zysa moxda ale.
It coincided with that disaster in eighty seven...
da amas daemtxva main is, otxmocdavid cels moxda es.
y nqad teld ama, gugey qor nmcind, amka edernda.
The avalanche moved down just up to here, to the front of our door and stopped here.
zvavi mtlad akamde amovida, veni aris irdair, ak gaerda.
atxe e xola desma xomna, desma zarl xomna xlxid mag,
Fortunately, nothing bad.... it did not make any harm to people...
axla iseti cudi araperi ar uknia, xalxi ar dauzaralebia ("ara ra zarali uknia xalxistvis qvela"),
It moves down and the rocks are falling into pieces...
anri i anri ale ikannen ser meyad, xernix or.
it moves down and down permanenty and rocks are taling into pieces...
